====setup pages========

1-create model

2-create controller
php artisan make:controller PostController -r

3-create modelFolder
in ../resources/views
create Post
and file index.blade.php

http://127.0.0.1:8000/Post
in web.php
write Route::resource('post', 'PostController');

in controller
write :
use \App\Post;
  $posts = Post::all();
        return view('post.index',compact('posts'));
    

